name: Menu of Plots
description: A menu of plotter drawing options. DM file names you like plus color you want me on twitter @tburtonwood. Each plot is a single color with archival ink on bristol and costs 3 Tez. Final drawing will be on 11 x 17 inch bristol. Plots will be drawn using Axi Draw drawing machine consecutively on top of each other. . Send me your shipping address and i'll calculate shipping cost. I'll also make you a 1/1 NFT photograph of the drawing for free.
